Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,December, 1923
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Odate Town Akita Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kakita from the\Nagricultural engineering section
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's some blizzard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably take till morning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They are borned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks\N- Make yourself comfortable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The male is purebred from\NOnoda Gorozaemon's place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a fine litter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Our chief engineer, Mr. Mase,\Nwas asked by his mentor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ueno Hidejiro of Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To find him an Akita puppy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When Aka was born
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a snowstorm\Nfor three days and nights
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:03:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We almost thought\Nour house would collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They are borned
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,HACHI-KO MONOGATARI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When you suddenly yelled out,\N"They are born!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought your wife had given birth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got five kids
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't handle another one
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the house
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ueno is one of our country"s
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Top agricultural engineers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's very' fond of dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When I visited him last year,\Nhe had just lost his dog
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A female Akita...\Nnot a purebred though
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He mentioned then that he\Nwanted a purebred next time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be overjoyed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll notify him right away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,May I use the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like Tokyo please
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo, Aoyama... number is 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His daughter is another dog lover
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Mr. Mase from the\NAkita prefectural office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Chizuko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents are in Hakone\Nat Tonosawa Hot Springs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They go there every' year
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy to take a message
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,An Akita?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're giving it to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was born this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A fine looking pup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is December 16th
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So after the new year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll call my father right away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to get an Akita puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean "again"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a purebred Akita!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I must call Father.\NWhat's the number in Hakone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, a singing frog
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter is on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I put the call\Nthrough to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A man from the Akita prefectural office\N...what was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mase
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Mr. Mase called
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful Akita puppy\Nwas born this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that you had asked for one
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mase was there when Gonsuke died
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd send me an Akita
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just asked him to keep us in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No more dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well...\Nit was a sad-time when Gonsuke died
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you cried
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's not get another dog
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mase really wants us to have it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want it,\NI'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted a purebred Akita
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She says that, but I'm the one\Nwho'll have to take care of it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when she found Gonsuke\Nin front of the train station
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to do everything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hate dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate cats AND dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me when Gonsuke died that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't have any more dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chizuko insists
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm opposed to it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a purebred this time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Purebred or mixed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go through\Nthat sadness again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuko says she'll take care of it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's snowing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay healthy now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they like him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out.\NDon't forget to pick up the dog
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- I pick up the dog.\N- Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I intended to go to the station with you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I changed my mind an hour ago
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to a concert at Hiblya Park
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tsumoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an idea
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always so fickle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he? It's urgent
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! Sorry'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't break it, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a dog arriving at 3P. M.\Nat Shibuya Station
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one besides Gonsuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonsuke died last year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...\NI took him to the crematory' myself
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's from Akita,\Nit must be an Akita breed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,With a tail that curls tight
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry' to interrupt
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against having a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miss Chizuko loves them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,People who love animals are kind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate dogs because
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always your duty\Nto clean the doghouse
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Chizuko is so mean
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She was supposed to go\Nto the station with me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But suddenly, she changed\Nher mind to go to a concert
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That fellow... her fiance came
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally! She'd prefer him to a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go to the station with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That face of yours would scare dogs more
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you're afraid of dogs too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come off it! At least a dog\Nis better than a cat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Feed a dog for three days\Nand it'll be loyal for life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can feed a cat for three years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it still won't care a whit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Saikichi, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a box... where was it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Odate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from Odate... a dog
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your seal, please
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have it with me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! This is for Ueno Hidejiro
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know Professor Ueno?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you should!\NHe's a famous agricultural engineer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the seal, Kiku
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Recognize my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of clerk are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiku of Inarizaka is pretty\Nwell known in this area
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that, blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now do you still need my seal?\N- Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your head's full of lead!\NLike the railroad tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thumbprint will do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dead
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! The railway company\Nwill pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog they sent from Akita is dead
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The railway company's to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not taking a dead dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When live animals are transported
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The railway company\Nis not responsible if it dies
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sailichi went to pick it up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Chizuko go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She went to a concert with Mr. Morlyama
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a bad omen\Nat the start of a new year
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Another dog's funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bound to happen...\Nafter riding a shaky train for two days
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kiku
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Prof...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The pup's dead
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, pup?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get some milk
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor little thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the journey was too long
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was against this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dead, Prof...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the puppy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:19:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The puppy's here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- You've been back?\N- I am back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the puppy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go and see it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You traveled so far
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be responsible for the puppy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about the puppy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,About Tsumoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you went to\Na concert with him today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He has something to discuss with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what he wants
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants me to get\Nanother friend into college
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't believe\Nin backdoor admissions
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free this coming Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's waiting outside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want any
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you show him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very' thoughtless of you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.30,0:23:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.60,0:23:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuko is with child
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:24:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I'm responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you angry'?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, after hearing whose child it is
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.63,0:24:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood pressure has gone down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.24,0:24:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.84,0:24:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for her hand in marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.95,0:24:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.59,0:24:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.99,0:24:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's best to have\Nthe ceremony right away
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.61,0:25:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.15,0:25:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.69,0:25:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.53,0:25:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking healthy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.90,0:25:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a name yet
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't choose a name\Nlike Gonsuke again
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.61,0:25:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't go nameless
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.55,0:25:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...\Nyour forelegs are firmly grounded
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.82,0:25:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the character\Nfor number eight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.16,0:25:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll name you Hachi as in 8
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.07,0:26:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.67,0:26:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We just got an Akita dog.\NWill you take it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.11,0:26:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.81,0:26:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're born in the year of the monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.31,0:26:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the boar
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.69,0:27:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A former student now\Nat the Akita prefectural office
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.49,0:27:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sent it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.49,0:27:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter wanted to keep it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.80,0:27:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But she'll be getting married soon
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.20,0:27:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She is your only daughter, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.24,0:27:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.04,0:27:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I had hoped to adopt a son-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.55,0:27:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But her fiance is also an only child
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.65,0:27:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it won't work
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.59,0:27:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're getting married\Nin a bit of a hurry'
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.22,0:27:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,On the 29th of this month
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.00,0:27:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you honor us by attending?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.00,0:27:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you also
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.99,0:28:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ueno Chizuko
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.56,0:28:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you take this man
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.99,0:28:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To be your lawfully wedded husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.10,0:28:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To have and to hold
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.07,0:28:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To love and to cherish
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.30,0:28:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To honor and obey
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.34,0:29:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In sickness and in health\Ntill death to you part?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.75,0:29:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I do
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.92,0:30:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuko didn't even shed a tear
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.39,0:30:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed your eyes were watery' though
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.70,0:30:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When she said good bye\Nfrom the train window
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.30,0:30:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The sadness suddenly hit me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.84,0:30:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That my little girl was being taken away
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.75,0:30:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Were they tears of bitterness then?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.82,0:30:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tears of bitterness, joy, sadness...\Nall at once
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.99,0:31:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they've checked\Ninto the inn by now
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.87,0:31:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was their honeymoon
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.57,0:31:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They could've gone farther than Atami
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.21,0:31:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumoru wanted to save money
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.82,0:31:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's very' stingy for his age
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.56,0:31:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think she was pregnant
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.00,0:31:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd have gotten pregnant\Nsooner or later
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.70,0:31:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just sooner
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.67,0:31:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was quite shocked by the whole thing
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.24,0:31:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What amazed me was the way she said
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.38,0:31:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm not taking the dog"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.22,0:31:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So bluntly, right before Morlyama
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.82,0:32:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When she offered all\Nher love to Morlyama
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.96,0:32:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but stare at her
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.53,0:32:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He was quite speechless too,\Nso I guess it worked
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.44,0:32:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuko was only saying\Nwhat was in her heart
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.68,0:32:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.21,0:32:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.28,0:32:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do about Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.72,0:32:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuko asked me to take care of it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.20,0:32:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.53,0:32:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty adamant
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.64,0:32:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not willing to share your love either
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.98,0:33:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Spin three times and bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.96,0:33:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Spin three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.56,0:33:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Spin and bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.49,0:33:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.70,0:33:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ogata!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.33,0:33:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tease the dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.44,0:34:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only a pup.\NHe doesn't know any tricks yet
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.97,0:34:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't keep dogs\Nso they can perform tricks
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.04,0:34:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourself in the dog's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.95,0:34:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi is hungry'! Hurry' and feed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.59,0:34:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already eaten, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.96,0:34:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice trip
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.03,0:34:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch Hachi while I'm away
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.04,0:34:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will you be away?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.97,0:34:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cultivating the area now
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.87,0:34:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to check the progress\Nso about four or five days
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.12,0:34:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as people have rights,\Ncanines have rights too
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.92,0:34:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll respect Hachi's rights
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.06,0:34:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we're going to give him away
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.00,0:35:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We must protect his rights\Nwhile he's staying here
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.68,0:35:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some tea, Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.17,0:35:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.34,0:35:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.12,0:35:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sailichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.03,0:36:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.66,0:36:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi, if you want\Nyour rights to be respected
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.34,0:36:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so naughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.74,0:36:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Babies have excess energy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.18,0:36:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't sit still
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.65,0:36:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How old is the little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.95,0:36:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Three months
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.32,0:36:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine! Becoming a father at his age!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.60,0:36:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry'!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.65,0:36:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.48,0:37:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing well
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.92,0:37:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.96,0:37:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you ruined your mistress's garden
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.50,0:37:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.00,0:37:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Hachi has grown
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.71,0:37:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only been away five days
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.48,0:37:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see signs of intelligence in\Nthose eyes of yours, Hachi
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.32,0:37:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.16,0:37:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.79,0:37:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It' better to give him away\Nwhile he's small
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.03,0:37:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.87,0:37:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be our dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.44,0:37:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.84,0:38:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I won't send you anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.05,0:38:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.33,0:38:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a cute dog
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.27,0:39:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, Hachi
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.09,0:40:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.97,0:40:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.14,0:40:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's growing so fast
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.91,0:40:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.40,0:41:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hachi
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.71,0:41:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go on home
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.31,0:42:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.85,0:42:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you didn't chew on grass
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.92,0:42:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go to the station\Nagain this evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.74,0:42:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, it's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.11,0:42:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, look
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.13,0:42:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.00,0:42:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Waited for me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.54,0:43:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some dog
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.45,0:43:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.31,0:43:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like it'll stop
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.82,0:43:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if the dog's here
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.35,0:44:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.31,0:44:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.02,0:44:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.25,0:44:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming, Hachi.\NEven in this snow
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.80,0:45:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, happy new year
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.97,0:45:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy new year
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.24,0:45:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy new year
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.61,0:45:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Same to you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.32,0:46:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't he grown big?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.65,0:46:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.59,0:46:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it all right to bring him\Nin this cold weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.32,0:46:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.79,0:46:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come inside, Chizuko
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.00,0:46:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't Hachi grown so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.90,0:46:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Catching fleas suits you, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.74,0:46:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is number 33
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.81,0:46:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me carry' him
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.69,0:46:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Toru's gotten so heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.66,0:46:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't talk yet
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.86,0:46:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NHe's only three months old
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.06,0:46:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Professor been at it since morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.50,0:46:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a research project with him
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.07,0:46:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how he is
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.84,0:47:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he gets started he can't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.88,0:47:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Father loves Hachi\Nmore than his own grandson
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.88,0:47:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.48,0:47:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Hachi accompanies him\Nto the station daily
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.09,0:47:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.19,0:47:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And goes back at sundown to meet him
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.06,0:47:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi doesn't wear a watch,\Nbut he knows the time
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.47,0:47:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.20,0:47:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep well
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.44,0:47:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we play some cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.74,0:47:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cards, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.71,0:47:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Better still, run a bath for me
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.72,0:47:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.52,0:47:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just fine, thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.30,0:48:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He amazes me
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.14,0:48:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he bathe with Hachi all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.37,0:48:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Always... after catching the fleas
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.91,0:48:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Better watch out, Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.11,0:48:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Hachi will take Father's love from you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.02,0:48:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.86,0:48:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.63,0:48:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.50,0:48:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.64,0:48:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi might catch cold,\Nso close the window
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.82,0:50:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're soaking wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.95,0:50:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.96,0:50:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even notice a storm brewing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.30,0:50:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll warm you up in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.91,0:50:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.49,0:51:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here where it's warm
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.87,0:51:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right here
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.85,0:53:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.28,0:53:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.03,0:53:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.33,0:53:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you can say?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.20,0:53:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you prefer Hachi to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.00,0:53:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.71,0:53:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.32,0:54:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,21-May-25
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.16,0:54:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.30,0:54:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.94,0:54:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.56,0:54:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.10,0:54:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go on home
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.42,0:55:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.11,0:56:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi! Settle down!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.78,0:56:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.76,0:56:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.49,0:56:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're barking so much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.20,0:56:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.35,0:56:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The second stage can be recognized
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.06,0:56:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flooding that occurs\Nevery' five or ten years
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.76,0:56:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This circumstance is unusual
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.47,0:57:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The third stage would be
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.17,0:57:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The most critical range
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.01,0:57:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So called the pro...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.28,0:57:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Probable maximum
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.86,0:57:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This probable...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.30,0:57:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.27,0:57:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.41,0:57:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.58,1:00:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.16,1:04:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With the professor gone,\Nthis house is too big for me
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.10,1:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll be going to live with Chizuko
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.91,1:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't they come to here to live?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.91,1:04:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuko thinks this house is too dreary'
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.12,1:04:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She is so indifferent
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.15,1:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She was born in this house, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.72,1:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I still sense my husband's\Npresence in this house...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.76,1:04:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes, it gets unbearable
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.90,1:04:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to sell this house
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.14,1:05:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have worked here for many years
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.65,1:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must let you go now
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.82,1:05:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but I'll pay\Nyou half a year's salary
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.33,1:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So please start giving\Nsome thought to your future
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.47,1:05:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go back home to Narashino
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.18,1:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sailichi?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.48,1:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll return to Shizuoka
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.22,1:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to have\Na memento of the professor
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.26,1:05:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you want in particular?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.17,1:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like his hat
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.27,1:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The fedora?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.74,1:06:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the silk hat
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.65,1:06:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.15,1:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Oyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.15,1:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a pair of his shoes
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.09,1:06:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For your father?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.42,1:06:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ever marry' and have a son
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.99,1:06:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let him wear it
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.93,1:06:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And tell him that it belonged\Nto the good professor
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.10,1:06:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When he went on his walks,\NI loved to watch his back
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.12,1:06:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.66,1:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye, Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.53,1:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye, Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.20,1:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.97,1:07:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.91,1:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.08,1:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.44,1:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Missus!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.12,1:08:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you taking Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.26,1:08:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuko says that seeing Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.83,1:08:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Will only remind her of her father
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.33,1:08:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an uncle in Asakusa
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.17,1:08:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd ask him to take Hachi in
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.47,1:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Maybe that's for the best
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.81,1:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello!\N- Hello!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.12,1:09:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a day off from the office\Nto help with the moving
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.49,1:09:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So did I. Let's do it then
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.02,1:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall we do with Father's books?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.83,1:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have no use for books\Non agriculture and cultivation
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.36,1:09:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it to the used books shop
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.17,1:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, come in
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.50,1:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a dilemma\Nabout where to start first
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.64,1:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get rid of anything old
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.68,1:09:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll clean out his study
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.15,1:09:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiku, can you help upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.66,1:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got a lot of young helpers
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.36,1:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All strong and spirited
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.96,1:09:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've got our hands full\Nwithout any pets
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.17,1:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But just leave him. I'll do what I can
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.07,1:10:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.98,1:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He eats anything people eat
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.22,1:10:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One can never tell what the future holds
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.59,1:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The professor was the\Npicture of health, yet...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.08,1:10:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.62,1:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Be good now
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.33,1:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.73,1:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.83,1:11:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Hachi is doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.07,1:11:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a worrywart
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.41,1:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.51,1:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're home
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.01,1:11:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you eat yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.78,1:11:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother scolded me that\NI should wait for my husband
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.48,1:12:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The foreign office keeps unusual hours
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.42,1:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So next time, please don't wait for me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.16,1:12:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a bath?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.62,1:12:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want dinner first
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.36,1:12:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandmother's here to stay, Toru
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.27,1:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How was Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.93,1:12:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I left him with my uncle in Asakusa
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.14,1:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready, so please wash up
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.54,1:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How old is this house?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.57,1:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,About 20 years
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.57,1:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It belonged to a college professor?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.44,1:12:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, an agriculture professor\Nat Imperial University
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.01,1:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He was world reknown
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.42,1:13:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so nice and bright\Nwith all the windows
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.12,1:13:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sturdy for an old house
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.26,1:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the price is right, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.36,1:13:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The missus is a kind lady
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.27,1:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she lower the price any more?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.05,1:13:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi! What's the idea!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.39,1:13:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were in Asakusa
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.52,1:13:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.79,1:13:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate dogs!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.56,1:13:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It belonged to the late professor.\NHis name's Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.90,1:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If this dog's going to come around,\NI won't buy this house!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.93,1:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry'
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.70,1:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This dog stays with a relative in Asakusa
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.51,1:14:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean he walked from\NAsakusa to Shibuya?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.94,1:14:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so. He wouldn't ride a train
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.28,1:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry' about this dog
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.69,1:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think about the house
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.32,1:14:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's right, please buy it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.19,1:14:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember though, get rid of the dog!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.06,1:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That dog has no personality
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.27,1:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Never reacts to a thing I say
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.43,1:14:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just turns around and starts to whine
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.37,1:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He bites off the chain and runs away
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.68,1:14:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, leave him here again
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.62,1:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he runs away, that's it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.47,1:16:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Set that up next to the bureau
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.44,1:16:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't scratch it!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.56,1:16:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.16,1:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.17,1:16:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That felt good!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.11,1:16:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I chopped up the doghouse for firewood
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.21,1:16:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a fine day... perfect for moving
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.92,1:17:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.06,1:17:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.34,1:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi, I want you to listen well
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.28,1:18:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your master is dead
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.52,1:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And this house was sold to someone else
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.46,1:18:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The new owner can't stand dogs
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.36,1:18:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to wander about here
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.83,1:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll chop your head off with his hatchet
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.44,1:18:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.48,1:18:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my house then
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.78,1:18:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care for dogs myself
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.35,1:18:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've known each other a long time
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.13,1:18:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.40,1:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,London, England?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.77,1:19:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as a first secretary'
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.61,1:19:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll attend to the new ambassador
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.88,1:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going too?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.05,1:19:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be returning to\Nmy hometown in Wakayama
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.42,1:19:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The professor's old home?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.19,1:19:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No... he had no other relatives
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.56,1:19:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But my mother still lives
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.97,1:19:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember...\Nsomewhere near the beach, was it?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.87,1:19:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a whaling town
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.61,1:19:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I'd love to see\Na live whale spouting water!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.52,1:19:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,About Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.45,1:19:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you taking him?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.32,1:19:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take him in?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.96,1:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have a cat...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.96,1:20:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of him
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.60,1:20:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you didn't want a dog!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.37,1:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But Missus can't take Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.71,1:20:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.81,1:20:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi was bred in Akita
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.35,1:20:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that! So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.48,1:20:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Akita is a cold place
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.08,1:20:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakayama is down south...\Nwhere they catch whales
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.35,1:20:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog from Akita couldn't\Nadjust to the warm weather
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.33,1:20:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I never met a woman who could talk more
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.80,1:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiku, please take care of Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.03,1:20:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be so relieved if you'd agree
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.30,1:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I will
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.01,1:20:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my way of repaying\Nthe late professor
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.82,1:21:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi's gone
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.96,1:21:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.86,1:21:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Around this time,\Nhe's always at the train station...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.30,1:21:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting by the exit
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.29,1:21:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.76,1:21:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get your ticket
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.24,1:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.84,1:21:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your master's not coming back any more
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.99,1:22:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to Wakayama
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.93,1:22:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've asked Kiku to take care of you
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.48,1:22:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye, Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.50,1:22:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.54,1:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.33,1:23:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought\Nyou'd agree to take Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.50,1:23:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate dogs
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.63,1:23:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a fool
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.64,1:23:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She has her mother to\Ntake care of back home
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.24,1:23:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She couldn't take this big\Nthing with her
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.78,1:23:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.58,1:23:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you understand\Nsimple human kindness?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.89,1:23:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Well, don't brag so much!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.06,1:23:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting senile lately!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.43,1:23:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! How dare you say that to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.46,1:24:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What "fool"?!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.70,1:24:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You called me...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.91,1:24:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A 'fool' first...!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.38,1:24:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.86,1:24:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry' Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.37,1:24:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't take you back with me
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.37,1:24:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to take Sanae here
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.78,1:24:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cancelled the lease\Nfor the house too
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.62,1:24:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.39,1:24:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.09,1:25:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong,\Nso don't lose to those stray dogs
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.96,1:25:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be the leader of a pack
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.77,1:25:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.11,1:25:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stray dogs run free
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.64,1:25:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So be free and live proud
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.51,1:25:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.76,1:25:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.59,1:25:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.15,1:25:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be waiting for his master
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.92,1:26:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't realize that his master's dead
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.92,1:26:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Admirable dog
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.96,1:26:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He comes every' day at the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.13,1:26:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a dumb dog
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.91,1:26:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry'
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.71,1:26:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come... I'll give you something
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.65,1:27:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.18,1:27:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiro died
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.61,1:27:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing. He's so skinny
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.60,1:28:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a year now
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.87,1:28:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for a master who won't return
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.01,1:28:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching him is painful
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.58,1:28:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wait for someone who won't come?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.82,1:28:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi wants to wait
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.49,1:28:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.35,1:29:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,December, 1928
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.22,1:29:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here again
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.29,1:29:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Let him wait
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.33,1:29:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's useless
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.66,1:29:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.30,1:29:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi doesn't care
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.89,1:30:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.16,1:30:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already. He's not coming back
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.10,1:30:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's raining
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.07,1:30:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here and have a bite
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.14,1:30:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a reporter with Asahi Shimbun
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.92,1:30:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Man's Best Friend"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.22,1:30:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dogs waits loyally for a master\Nwho won't return"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.34,1:30:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.51,1:31:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I rushed over when I read the newspaper
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.59,1:31:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been waiting for\Nyour master every' day?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.19,1:31:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how dirty you are
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.60,1:31:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How you must've suffered
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.60,1:31:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the missus?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.24,1:31:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This dog comes every' day in the evening
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.25,1:31:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband really loved him...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.82,1:31:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts to see him like this
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.60,1:31:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry',\Nbut we don't have a place for dogs
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.17,1:32:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Any corner will do
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.47,1:32:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the dog\Nthat was in the papers?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.74,1:32:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.65,1:32:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the loyal dog, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.49,1:32:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.86,1:32:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the late owner, Professor Ueno
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.19,1:32:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll let this\Nloyal dog stay the night
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.50,1:32:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't bite though
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.33,1:32:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he won't
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.80,1:32:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi is a good boy
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.74,1:33:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.78,1:33:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was here awhile ago
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.41,1:35:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi disappeared from the inn
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.62,1:35:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three days now
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.12,1:35:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he thought\NI'd give him away again
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.60,1:35:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi wants to stay here
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.20,1:35:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Free and unchained
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.91,1:36:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel his eyes on me
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.38,1:36:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be going
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.22,1:36:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hachi comes, please feed him
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.42,1:36:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't accept!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.52,1:36:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.09,1:36:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.12,1:36:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad dog! Coming here again!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.56,1:36:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.85,1:37:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Scat!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.63,1:38:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Two Japanese army is still fighting
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.23,1:38:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our team is entering the city
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.47,1:38:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- It is really exiting.\N- I don't want to see this
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.98,1:38:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.55,1:38:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor thing!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.42,1:39:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the mutt the paper wrote about?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.69,1:39:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a name... It's Hachi
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.33,1:39:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he's not waiting for his master
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.43,1:39:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a freeloader waiting for food
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.43,1:39:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,These foul pests should be put to sleep
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.14,1:39:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say mister, you're the one\Nwith a foul heart
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.41,1:39:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you face\Na customer and say that!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.91,1:39:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no customer of mine!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.29,1:39:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.40,1:39:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your money!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.60,1:39:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.11,1:39:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.81,1:39:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.31,1:40:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat all you want!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.45,1:40:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat up
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.09,1:40:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.86,1:40:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,May, 1934
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.11,1:42:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.44,1:42:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
